7874	  \(\operatorname{restrictFunctor} f : Y.\mathrm{Modules} \to X.\mathrm{Modules}\) is
7875	  naturally isomorphic to the module pullback functor \(f^* = \operatorname{pullback} f\). In
7876	  particular \(f^*\mathcal{M} \cong \mathcal{M}.\operatorname{restrict} f\) for every
